[*] --> Archived
Archived --> Active : reject
Archived : entry / log notification
Active --> Created : confirm
Created --> OnHold : submit
OnHold --> Draft : submit
Draft --> Shipped : confirm
Draft : entry / log notification
Shipped --> [*]
